title: Brady Quinn hands out Xmas gifts for playoff teams (Football 12/26)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to talk about various Christmas things, different bowl games and whether Notre Dame can hang with Clemson. Then the guys give out Christmas presents for every single team who might still make the NFL playoffs.
